    The Pestana CR7 Marrakesh is a new and sophisticated hotel located on M Avenue, in Marrakesh, Morocco. Come and explore the exotic atmosphere of one of Africas largest cities, so close to the desert.
    The hotel is located a short distance from the historic city centre, offering an exceptional level of comfort and an atmosphere inspired by the Moroccan riads, which are the traditional local houses, with rooms and areas that are spacious, bright and romantic.
    The 174 rooms and suites are very spacious and equipped with everything you need for an unforgettable stay including unique decor, natural light and a 49-inch HD TV.
    In our restaurants, you can opt for an informal meal of tapas and drinks at the ground-floor bar or the Mediterranean dishes served on the Rooftop. It is also on the Rooftop that you will find the outdoor swimming pool and bar, both with incredible panoramic views of the Atlas mountains.
    To relax after a hectic day shopping at the souk or taking a camel tour, we suggest you spend an hour at our Spa, with its beauty and wellness treatments. You can also watch major sports events at our Sports Lounge & Bar.
    If you need an appropriate space for professional or personal matters, we have 5 meeting rooms available, equipped with audiovisual media to make each event a success.

    Hivernage

    Refined, modern Hivernage is known for nightlife, with a casino, cocktail lounges, hotel dance clubs and chic global restaurants with live music. The Royal Theatre, with domes and Ancient Egyptianstyle columns, stages concerts in an amphitheater. Nearby, the Menara Gardens, with a huge reflecting pool and mountains in the background, date to the 12th century, and El-Harti Park has fountains and a rose garden.
